00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:58.160
I secretly took his sachet.

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:00.040
I thought that if I got exposed,

00:04:00.680 --> 00:04:02.920
I would have a way out.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:08.440
